Package fr.iutvalence.info.but.r2_01.labyrinthGame.core

Class StepInfo

java.lang.Object
fr.iutvalence.info.but.r2_01.labyrinthGame.core.StepInfo
public class StepInfo extends Object
Class representing a step of labyrinth game (step count, robot initial position and heading, action, robot resulting position and heading).
